reviewText: This is the boom in the old days and it is still is the boom

We enjoy Perry Mason; and wanted the movies we recorded from TV on DVD.
Love all Perry mason movies great the characters are greatkeeps you on the edge of your seat fun to watch. Free
Perry mason always a favorite back in the day and now today i am enjoying it all over again
Always happy with Perry Mason DVD's.  One of my favorite series. Both the regular series and the Return series.  He was one of a kind and Raymond Burr was the perfect actor to play Perry Mason.
Raymond Burr never disappoints even in his mature years to provide top self entertainment. His movies are classic Perry Mason.

Excellent condition. It is cheaper to buy the 12 Double Feature sets than to buy the larger 6 movies sets. If you are a Perry Mason fan, these are a must for your collection. And the sets are produced in order of when each movie was shown. I will be watching these often.
